title: Will Tulsi Gabbard be appointed to the Trump Administration via recess appointment before Aug 1, 2025?
rules_primary: If Tulsi Gabbard is appointed to the Trump Administration in any role via recess appointment in a position that would otherwise require Senate confirmation before Aug 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
